DetailedDescription: A war hammer can be used to attack another player, it has a 20% chance of killing them.
The war hammer has a separate 75% chance of causing the target a concussion
A concussed player may accidentally visit a neighbour of their night target, the target and each neighbour all have a 33% chance of being visited
You cannot use a war hammer and another item on the same night
A Tysta Rune allows you to silence a player, making their vote count as 0 the next day.
Holding it will make you appear as a Witch Craft user to intel checks.
After use, a Rune must recharge and can be used again by you three nights later.
If you pass the Rune to a different player they will be able to use it immediately.

Description: A Potion of Clarity allows you to find out a player's alignment

DetailedDescription: A Vahetus Rune allows you to swap avatars with another player.
Holding it will make you appear as a Witch Craft user to intel checks.
After use, a Rune must recharge and can be used again by you three nights later.
If you pass the Rune to a different player they will be able to use it immediately.
Lich spells are etched into the skin torn from freshly killed undead. They can be used to increase the power of Liches currently in the game.
Lich spells take effect from the night after they are cast.
You may choose from the following options -
1) Give each Decay token a 25% chance of spreading to a randomly selected neighbour when the Lich triggers the Decay
2) Give dead Undead with decay a 25% chance of being revived when a Lich triggers the Decay
3) Make any player with decay appear as Undead to checking roles
If you are brewing a potion that takes longer than 1 night, you will not see these options until the potion has been completed
